reviewText: Secrets of the Founders?  The world already knew they were Masons and that Masonic influences can be found in everything from the Constitution to the currency.  The rest of this show is hearsay, false accusations, and, quite frankly, garbage!  And this show was produced by a channel that calls themselves History?  What a joke!  I guess I should have known better  these are the same people that created Ancient Aliens.
